1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,450
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,610 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:34,740 --> 00:00:35,650
It's windy here.

4
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,580
Let's head back.

5
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:40,210
Okay.

6
00:00:47,310 --> 00:00:49,730
Congrats on getting back together.

7
00:00:50,290 --> 00:00:53,850
Shouldn't you buy us a wedding dinner?

8
00:00:54,780 --> 00:00:55,570
Oh, wait.

9
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:57,350
You've already been married once.

10
00:00:57,930 --> 00:01:01,170
Then buy us drinks
for your baby's first month.

11
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:06,290
Oh.

12
00:01:06,980 --> 00:01:09,060
Did you sort out the security footage?

13
00:01:09,290 --> 00:01:10,900
Of course I did.

14
00:01:11,650 --> 00:01:12,650
You work fast.

15
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:13,980
Mm.

16
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:18,280
What are you doing?

17
00:01:18,290 --> 00:01:19,140
Why are you here?

18
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:20,620
I came to see Qiao Nian.

19
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,450
You've seen her.

20
00:01:26,540 --> 00:01:27,340
Now leave.

21
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:28,340
Hmph.

22
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:30,370
Do you own this place?

23
00:01:30,370 --> 00:01:32,620
You tell me to leave, so I leave? Funny.

24
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:33,570
Funny.

25
00:01:34,290 --> 00:01:35,090
Fine.

26
00:01:36,210 --> 00:01:37,260
Then I'll take her away.

27
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,420
You should give up now.

28
00:01:52,090 --> 00:01:53,450
Don't make this harder on yourself.

29
00:01:56,930 --> 00:02:00,980
Once, a true love stood right
in front of Qiao Nian.

30
00:02:02,810 --> 00:02:04,060
But she didn't cherish it.

31
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:06,780
Only after she lost it

32
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:10,160
did she regret it deeply.

33
00:02:10,370 --> 00:02:13,650
Hey, why are you getting
all Romeo and Juliet?

34
00:02:17,130 --> 00:02:19,370
Actually, love

35
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:20,500
can be pretty simple.

36
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:23,580
You get it?

37
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:24,500
Of course.

38
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:26,460
I'm a dating sim addict.

39
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:28,970
And I've watched
way too many romance dramas.

40
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:31,090
Dating sim?

41
00:02:31,810 --> 00:02:34,650
Anyway, it means I cleared

42
00:02:34,650 --> 00:02:35,810
a relationship level.

43
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,130
Hmph!

44
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:48,930
Go home and rest.

45
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:50,580
I'll stay with Grandpa.

46
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:51,990
Everything will be fine.

47
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,530
You should go home too.

48
00:02:53,650 --> 00:02:55,620
I'll watch over the old man.

49
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:59,300
Then I'll leave it to you.

50
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:01,250
Alright. Go on.

51
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:02,130
Stop nagging.

52
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:03,340
Thanks.

53
00:03:08,130 --> 00:03:09,740
Hey, where are you going?

54
00:03:10,130 --> 00:03:10,900
I...

55
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,340
I need to protect Qiao Nian.

56
00:03:12,970 --> 00:03:16,020
Can't you tell the couple
has other things to do?

57
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:24,020
Do what?

58
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:28,210
You know... adult stuff.

59
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:35,020
You're hopeless.

60
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:39,060
Stay here and learn how to date from me.

61
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,630
(Affection +1.
You did that for me, right?)

62
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:56,780
If I keep playing,
I'll become romance-obsessed.

63
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:58,740
Aren't you already?

64
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:05,740
(Jiang Zechen,)

65
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,920
(tonight, you're mine.)

66
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,370
The hospital just called.

67
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:27,500
Grandpa's condition
has stabilized a lot.

68
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:31,300
He may wake up soon.

69
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:36,980
So take good care of yourself.

70
00:05:38,690 --> 00:05:39,500
Mm.

71
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:51,130
Nian, how have you been?

72
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:52,130
Dad,

73
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,930
what brings you here?

74
00:05:58,500 --> 00:05:59,500
Take a look at this.

75
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:04,570
Fifteen years ago,

76
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,740
your aunt signed this agreement with me.

77
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,500
(Party A: Jiang Xiao.
Party B: Qiao Wenjun.)

78
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,690
Back then, Qiao Group
was in financial trouble.

79
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:13,330
She came to me for money to save it.

80
00:06:13,740 --> 00:06:14,620
I agreed.

81
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,450
I invested two and a half billion.

82
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:19,010
But I had one condition.

83
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:22,130
Qiao Group couldn't have any scandals

84
00:06:22,130 --> 00:06:23,810
or a drop in stock price.

85
00:06:24,130 --> 00:06:27,540
Otherwise, you owe me
five billion in damages.

86
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:29,540
Five billion?

87
00:06:29,770 --> 00:06:32,420
Don't rush. I'm not done yet.

88
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:39,060
Or you give me 60%
of Qiao Group's shares.

89
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,450
- You...
- Dad.

90
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:50,810
So you made Qiao Wenjun
fake the product records.

91
00:06:51,130 --> 00:06:52,690
You created the breach, didn't you?

92
00:06:52,690 --> 00:06:54,620
Oh, Nian.

93
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:56,890
You can't just say that.

94
00:06:56,890 --> 00:06:58,010
Do you have proof?

95
00:06:58,570 --> 00:06:59,980
Then answer me.

96
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:03,130
The factory files with quality issues.

97
00:07:03,450 --> 00:07:04,540
How did you know about them?

98
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:10,500
Since we're talking about it,

99
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,180
fine.

100
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:15,250
I was the one who told you
to find the documents.

101
00:07:16,130 --> 00:07:18,540
But even if I arranged all this,

102
00:07:18,690 --> 00:07:20,300
I still helped you, didn't I?

103
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:22,810
Nian,

104
00:07:23,930 --> 00:07:26,450
I don't want to make
things hard for you.

105
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:29,180
After all, we're family.

106
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:32,620
But business is business.

107
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,370
Even family has
to keep accounts straight.

108
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:37,740
Your family signed this agreement.

109
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:40,500
Now you're the only Qiao
left in the company.

110
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:43,220
So you're the one I have
to collect from.

111
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,370
Fine.

112
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:53,220
I'll meet the deadline in the contract.

113
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:56,740
Within one month,
I'll pay all the damages.

114
00:07:58,130 --> 00:07:59,250
Good.

115
00:08:06,930 --> 00:08:09,770
Then I'll be waiting for good news,

116
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:11,330
my dear daughter-in-law.

117
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:29,250
You useless idiot!

118
00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:30,450
Get lost!

119
00:08:32,010 --> 00:08:32,820
(Zechen!)

120
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:43,750
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

121
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:51,630
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

122
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:55,470
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

123
00:08:55,990 --> 00:08:59,270
♪Where this ends♪

124
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:06,550
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

125
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:10,880
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

126
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:14,000
♪Love turns into pain♪

127
00:09:14,070 --> 00:09:18,190
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

128
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:21,830
♪Yet I still want you close♪

129
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:26,000
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

130
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:29,310
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

131
00:09:29,310 --> 00:09:33,880
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

132
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:40,190
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

133
